summary: Founder of IntraMart Corporation on October of 1997 in San Jose California, IntraMart has been providing world class IT services in all areas of Information Technology throughout North America. From the requirements gathering to business intelligence delivery, IntraMart provides expertise in architecture and development in every step through the process with talent in ETL, DW, and BI products.In 2003 Greg expanded IntraMart to Aguascalientes Mexico and hired Alberto Jimenez to develop the company throughout Latin America. With IntraMart providing “Same-Time” services as an outsourcing alternative, companies of the likes of GE and PetSmart have taken advantage our temporary staff augmentation to improve both productivity and bottom line.Having our roots and kick start in San Jose California, In October of 2005 Greg moved IntraMart headquarters to the Phoenix area and is continuing to expand IntraMart throughout North America. With main offices in Scottsdale Arizona, Monterrey and Aguascalientes Mexico, we are continuing to grow as a world class Information Technology Service Company. IntraMart now has offices throughout North America and India and is looking to expand it's service offerings while maintaining our commitment to our clients.Specialties: Architecture and development in Business Intelligence, ETL, Data warehousing, eLearning, Custom Applications development.
